# ----- AR Maintenance Backend -----
This backend API supports an AR-based maintenance system for public transport environments. 
It handles fault reporting, tool tracking, and secure communication between the frontend 
and database.

## ----- Tech Stack -----
- Node.js
- Express.js
- Nodemon
- dotenv

## ----- Installation -----

1. Clone the repository:
git clone <https://github.com/Dom056/Tech-Innovations-Backend-Code.git>

2. Navigate into the project folder:
cd backend

3. Install dependencies:
npm install

## ----- Environment Variables -----

Create a `.env` file in the root directory and add:

PORT=5000
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

## ----- Running the Server -----

Start the development server with nodemon:

npm run devStart